{"settings":"{
	// ========= EDITOR  =====================================
	"editor.fontFamily": "ShureTechMono Nerd Font",
	"editor.codeActionsOnSave": {
		"source.fixAll": true,
		"source.organizeImports": true
	},
	"quokka.showCodeLensInOutputChannel": false,
	"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
	"editor.fontLigatures": true,
	"editor.cursorBlinking": "phase",
	"kite.showWelcomeNotificationOnStartup": false,
	"editor.minimap.enabled": false,
	"workbench.editor.untitled.hint": "hidden",
	"explorer.confirmDelete": false,
	"explorer.confirmDragAndDrop": true,
	"editor.wordWrap": "wordWrapColumn",
	"editor.guides.bracketPairs": "active",
	"editor.language.brackets": [],
	"editor.scrollbar.horizontalScrollbarSize": 4,
	"editor.scrollbar.verticalScrollbarSize": 5,
	"editor.smoothScrolling": true,
	"editor.cursorSmoothCaretAnimation": "on",
	"editor.cursorStyle": "block-outline",
	"editor.lineNumbers": "relative",
	"editor.renderWhitespace": "all",
	"editor.stickyScroll.enabled": true,
	"editor.bracketPairColorization.independentColorPoolPerBracketType": true,
	"editor.formatOnPaste": false,
	"editor.formatOnSave": true,
	"editor.language.colorizedBracketPairs": [],
	"editor.formatOnType": false,
	"editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
	"editor.stablePeek": true,
	"editor.linkedEditing": true,
	"editor.foldingImportsByDefault": true,
	"editor.hover.delay": 250,
	"editor.lineHeight": 1.54,
	"editor.letterSpacing": -1,
	"editor.padding.bottom": 25,
	"editor.padding.top": 25,
	"editor.tabSize": 5,
	"editor.accessibilityPageSize": 20,
	"editor.fontWeight": "800",
	"editor.fontVariations": true,
	"interactiveSession.editor.fontFamily": "FiraCode Nerd Font",
	"editor.largeFileOptimizations": true,

	"workbench.editor.tabCloseButton": "off",
	"workbench.editor.wrapTabs": true,
	"workbench.editor.titleScrollbarSizing": "large",
	"workbench.editor.preferHistoryBasedLanguageDetection": true,

	//============ EXPLORER ==================================
	"explorer.fileNesting.enabled": true,
	"editor.tokenColorCustomizations": {
		"[Vim Dark Hard]": {},
		"textMateRules": [
			{
				"name": "One Dark italic",
				"scope": ["comment", "entity.other.attribute-name", "keyword", "markup.underline.link", "storage.modifier", "storage.type", "string.url", "variable.language.super", "variable.language.this"],
				"settings": {
					"fontStyle": "italic"
				}
			},
			{
				"name": "One Dark italic reset",
				"scope": [
					"keyword.operator",
					"keyword.other.type",
					"storage.modifier.import",
					"storage.modifier.package",
					"storage.type.built-in",
					"storage.type.function.arrow",
					"storage.type.generic",
					"storage.type.java",
					"storage.type.primitive"
				],
				"settings": {
					"fontStyle": ""
				}
			}
		]
	},
	"explorer.openEditors.sortOrder": "alphabetical",

	//========== ERROR LENS =========================
	"errorLens.fontFamily": "FiraCode Nerd Font",
	"errorLens.fontSize": "13",
	"errorLens.fontStyleItalic": true,
	"errorLens.fontWeight": "600",
	"errorLens.borderRadius": "5px",
	"errorLens.excludeBySource": ["ts(7006)"],
	"errorLens.statusBarCommand": "goToLine",

	//======================================================================================
	"code-runner.clearPreviousOutput": true,

	// ========= TERMINAL ===============================================
	"terminal.integrated.fontSize": 12,
	"terminal.integrated.profiles.windows": {
		"PowerShell": {
			"source": "PowerShell",
			"icon": "terminal-powershell"
		},
		"Git Bash": {
			"source": "Git Bash"
		}
	},
	"terminal.integrated.enableMultiLinePasteWarning": false,
	"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows": "Git Bash",
	"terminal.integrated.copyOnSelection": true,
	"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "zsh",
	"terminal.integrated.enableBell": true,
	"terminal.integrated.fontWeight": "800",
	"terminal.integrated.fontWeightBold": "bold",
	"terminal.integrated.ignoreProcessNames": ["starship", "bash"],
	"terminal.integrated.automationProfile.windows": {
		"color": "terminal.ansiBlue"
	},
	"terminal.integrated.env.windows": {},
	"terminal.integrated.autoReplies": {},
	"terminal.integrated.tabs.defaultColor": "terminal.ansiCyan",
	"terminal.integrated.tabs.defaultIcon": "terminal-bash",
	"terminal.integrated.tabs.focusMode": "singleClick",
	"terminal.integrated.smoothScrolling": true,
	"terminal.integrated.minimumContrastRatio": 7,
	"terminal.integrated.localEchoStyle": "underlined",
	"terminal.external.windowsExec": "",
	"terminal.integrated.tabStopWidth": 5,
	"terminal.integrated.letterSpacing": 0.85,
	"terminal.integrated.lineHeight": 1.18,
	"terminal.integrated.tabFocusMode": false,
	"terminal.integrated.gpuAcceleration": "on",
	"terminal.integrated.splitCwd": "workspaceRoot",

	"debug.terminal.clearBeforeReusing": true,

	"terminal.integrated.": "xterm",
	"terminal.integrated.profiles.cwd": "",

	"debug.console.fontFamily": "FiraCode Nerd Font",
	"debug.javascript.terminalOptions": {},

	//======================== FILES =================================================
	"files.autoSave": "afterDelay",
	"files.autoSaveDelay": 5000,
	"files.exclude": {
		"**/__tests__": true,
		"**/.vscode": true,
		"**/build": true,
		"**/dist": true,
		"**/node_modules": true,
		"**/package-lock.json": true,
		"**/thunder-tests": true
	},

	// ==================== PRETTIER =====================================
	"prettier.trailingComma": "all",
	"prettier.useTabs": true,
	"prettier.printWidth": 220,
	"prettier.enableDebugLogs": true,
	"prettier.semi": false,
	"workbench.productIconTheme": "icons-carbon",

	//============== DATABASE EXTENSIONS ======================================
	"database-client.resultTheme": "stripe",
	"database-client.highlightSQLBlock": true,
	"database-client.showUser": true,
	"database-client.showTrigger": true,
	"database-client.showEvent": true,
	"database-client.showQuery": true,
	"database-client.showReverseSwitch": true,
	"database-client.escapedAllObjectName": true,
	"database-client.reloadAfterDML": true,
	"database-client.resultRowHeight": "28px",
	"database-client.saveConnectionExpandedState": true,

	//================= THUNDER CLIENT =================================================
	"thunder-client.saveToWorkspace": true,
	"thunder-client.httpLibrary": "axios",
	"thunder-client.httpVersion": "HTTP/2",
	"thunder-client.requestLayout": "Top/Bottom",
	"thunder-client.sidebar.defaultTab": "Collections",
	"thunder-client.editorFontSize": 12,
	"thunder-client.saveTokenPerEnvironment": true,
	"thunder-client.sidebar.showActivityFromCollection": true,

	//============== GIT ========================================================
	"git.terminalGitEditor": true,
	"git.ignoredRepositories": ["c:\\Users\\ASUS\\.vscode\\extensions\\stepsize.stepsize-1.0.1\\resources\\demo-repository"],
	"git.enableSmartCommit": true,
	"gitlens.currentLine.dateFormat": "",
	"gitlens.gitCommands.search.showResultsInSideBar": false,
	"git.openRepositoryInParentFolders": "always",

	//============= VIM =================================================
	"vim.textwidth": 240,
	"editor.wordWrapColumn": 240,
	"vim.commandLineModeKeyBindings": [],
	"vim.commandLineModeKeyBindingsNonRecursive": [],
	"vim.easymotion": true,
	"vim.insertModeKeyBindings": [
		{
			"before": ["<Capslock>"],
			"after": ["<Esc>"]
		}
	],
	"vim.normalModeKeyBindings": [],
	"vim.argumentObjectClosingDelimiters": [")", "]", "}"],
	"vim.argumentObjectOpeningDelimiters": ["(", "[", "{"],
	"vim.argumentObjectSeparators": [",", "."],
	"vim.cursorStylePerMode.insert": "line-thin",
	"vim.foldfix": true,
	"vim.handleKeys": {
		"<C-w>": false,
		// "<C-d>": true,
		"<C-s>": false,
		"<C-z>": false,
		// "<C-b>": false,
		"<C-a>": false,
		"<C-c>": false,
		"<C-x>": false,
		"<C-v>": false
	},
	"vim.highlightedyank.enable": true,
	"vim.cursorStylePerMode.normal": "block",
	"vim.digraphs": {},
	"vim.visualModeKeyBindings": [],

	"vim.camelCaseMotion.enable": true,
	"vim.highlightedyank.textColor": "#581845",
	"vim.highlightedyank.duration": 250,

	"vim.statusBarColorControl": true,
	"vim.statusBarColors.normal": "#1F618D",
	"vim.statusBarColors.insert": "#DE3163",
	"vim.statusBarColors.visualline": "#28B463",
	"vim.statusBarColors.commandlineinprogress": "#2E4053",
	"vim.highlightedyank.color": "#F8C8DC",
	"vim.showMarksInGutter": true,

	//=================================================================================
	"tabnine.experimentalAutoImports": true,
	"[javascript]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"emmet.includeLanguages": {
		"javascript": "javascriptreact"
	},
	"notebook.output.wordWrap": true,
	"bracket-pair-colorizer-2.depreciation-notice": false,
	"javascript.updateImportsOnFileMove.enabled": "always",
	"liveServer.settings.donotShowInfoMsg": true,
	"cSpell.userWords": ["showpin"],
	"autoimport.filesToScan": "**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}",

	"typescript.updateImportsOnFileMove.enabled": "always",
	"[dart]": {
		"editor.formatOnSave": true,
		"editor.formatOnType": true,
		"editor.rulers": [80],
		"editor.selectionHighlight": false,
		"editor.suggest.snippetsPreventQuickSuggestions": false,
		"editor.suggestSelection": "first",
		"editor.tabCompletion": "onlySnippets",
		"editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false
	},

	"window.openFilesInNewWindow": "default",

	"[json]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},

	"material-icon-theme.activeIconPack": "react_redux",
	"material-icon-theme.files.associations": {
		"*.ts": "typescript",
		"**.json": "json",
		"fileName.ts": "angular"
	},
	"material-icon-theme.folders.associations": {},
	"material-icon-theme.folders.color": "#2568db",
	"material-icon-theme.languages.associations": {},
	"rapidapi.terminalLink.enabled": false,
	"go.toolsManagement.autoUpdate": true,
	"react-native-tools.showUserTips": false,
	"[jsonc]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
	},
	"background.fullscreen": {
		"image": "https://wallpapercave.com/wp/wp2301613.jpg",
		"opacity": 0.7,
		"size": "cover",
		"interval": 0
	},

	"[typescript]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "vscode.typescript-language-features"
	},
	"css.lint.boxModel": "warning",
	"css.lint.duplicateProperties": "warning",
	"css.lint.float": "warning",
	"css.lint.fontFaceProperties": "error",
	"css.lint.idSelector": "error",
	"css.lint.important": "warning",
	"css.lint.ieHack": "warning",
	"css.lint.importStatement": "warning",
	"css.lint.unknownVendorSpecificProperties": "warning",
	"scss.lint.float": "warning",
	"less.lint.important": "warning",
	"less.lint.float": "warning",
	"totalTypeScript.hideAllTips": false,
	"totalTypeScript.hideBasicTips": false,
	"sqltools.connections": [],
	"workbench.startupEditor": "none",
	"notebook.breadcrumbs.showCodeCells": false,
	"grunt.autoDetect": "on",
	"workbench.colorCustomizations": {
		"statusBar.background": "#1F618D",
		"statusBar.noFolderBackground": "#1F618D",
		"statusBar.debuggingBackground": "#1F618D"
	},

	"typescript.format.insertSpaceAfterConstructor": true,
	"eslint.format.enable": true,
	"eslint.packageManager": "pnpm",
	"workbench.layoutControl.type": "menu",
	"mssql.enableQueryHistoryCapture": false,
	"[svg]": {
		"editor.defaultFormatter": "jock.svg"
	},
	"npm.enableRunFromFolder": true,

	"debug.javascript.defaultRuntimeExecutable": {
		"pwa-node": "node"
	},

	"vsicons.dontShowNewVersionMessage": true,
	"editor.guides.highlightActiveIndentation": "always",

	"[python]": {
		"editor.formatOnType": true
	},
	"scm.defaultViewMode": "tree",
	"scm.inputFontFamily": "FiraCode Nerd Font",

	"auto-close-tag.insertSpaceBeforeSelfClosingTag": true,

	"search.defaultViewMode": "tree",
	"search.maxResults": 1000,

	"workbench.layoutControl.enabled": false,
	"window.menuBarVisibility": "toggle",
	"workbench.iconTheme": "vscode-icons",
	"workbench.colorTheme": "Sweet Dracula Monokai",
	"editor.fontSize": 13.4,
	"terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "JetBrainsMonoNL Nerd Font",
	"editor.codeLensFontFamily": "FiraCode Nerd Font",
	"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.osx": "",
	"svelte.enable-ts-plugin": true,
	"prettier.singleAttributePerLine": true,
	"breadcrumbs.filePath": "last"
}"}
